 # Changelog
 
+## 2026-07-17 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S3-P02-T034 (first A0 adapter: State Council policy + national laws; NOT_DEPLOYED)
+
+- Thirty-fourth task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program and the first of S3-P02 (first A0 official adapters). Goal: parse the gov.cn State Council policy documents and national laws/regulations into the A0 template -- original title, 发文字号, issuing organ, typed dates (成文 written kept distinct from 发布 published), effectiveness status, and attachments. NOT_DEPLOYED, 0 recurring cloud cost; the adapter is not wired into the worker, and a live parse runs from the dev environment. Deliverables under arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/: tools/adapter_gov_policy.py (a GovCnPolicyConnector on the T031 SDK with parse_policy producing the typed-date A0 template, discover with a recoverable cursor, verification via the T033 identity verifier, and build_registry for both gov-cn-policy and gov-cn-fagui), ADAPTER_GOV_POLICY_SPEC.md, and evidence/ADP-S3-P02-T034/{fixtures/{policy_2016,policy_2020,policy_2024,policy_current,listing}.html, expected/*.json, real_parse_smoke.json}. Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S3-P02-T034/test-results/adapter_tests.txt, ACCEPTANCE = PASS, exit 0): the official original and attachments are replayable (the 2016, 2020, 2024, and current fixtures parse to their golden JSON, a second parse is byte-identical, and the attachments 0/0/1/2 are replayable); the date types are not confused (the written date equals 成文, the published date equals 发布, and the canonical doc_date is the published date, never swapped or collapsed); and the historical cursor is recoverable (discover finds four items across the eras, a cursor at 2020-12-21 resumes to only 2024-03-01 and 2026-07-10, and the cursor advances to the latest 2026-07-10). A live parse through the adapter confirmed three real gov.cn documents -- 国办发〔2020〕50号 (成文 2020-12-07 / 发布 2020-12-21), 国令第711号 (2019-04-03 / 2019-04-15), and 国办函〔2021〕132号 (成文 2021-12-22 / 发布 2022-01-04, a cross-year case that is exactly why the date types must not be confused) -- as a point-in-time artifact. The live parse ran from the dev environment, so 0 cloud cost; wiring the adapter into the worker cron later makes each fetch a Worker subrequest counted against the DIR-007 free tier. Cost (unknown != 0): new_requests 0, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
+
 ## 2026-07-17 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S3-P01-T033 (official identity verifier + A0 marking; closes S3-P01; NOT_DEPLOYED)
 
 - Thirty-third task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program and the LAST of S3-P01 (minimal official-source connector kernel). Goal: verify a source's officialness from four evidence signals -- an official .gov.cn domain, the host organization 主办单位, the government website directory, and the website ID code 网站标识码 -- and assign an authority level. NOT_DEPLOYED, 0 recurring cloud cost; a verifier and rules, not wired into the production enable flow. Deliverables under arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/: tools/official_identity.py (is_official_domain / is_central_domain, extract_evidence pulling host_org / id_code / ICP from a real footer, and verify_identity returning the authority level plus can_enable, discovery_only, manual_review, the evidence, and reasons), OFFICIAL_IDENTITY_SPEC.md, and evidence/ADP-S3-P01-T033/{identity_report.json, source_specs.json, real_identity_smoke.json}. Two hard rules are enforced: an unverified source cannot be enabled, and search or media sources are discovery-only and never receive A0. Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S3-P01-T033/test-results/identity_tests.txt, ACCEPTANCE = PASS, exit 0): a central .gov.cn domain with at least one official marker is A0 and enable-able (both a full-marker case and an id-code-only case), a non-central official domain is A1, media (even on a gov domain) and search and aggregator are discovery-only with no A0 and cannot be enabled, an official domain with no markers goes to manual_review and cannot be enabled, and a non-gov domain claiming official is unofficial and cannot be enabled; RULE 1 (unverified not enabled) and RULE 2 (search/media never A0) both hold. A live footer extraction confirmed the real www.gov.cn (主办单位 国务院办公厅, 网站标识码 bm01000001, 京ICP备05070218号 -> A0) and stats.gov.cn (bm36000002 -> A0) as a point-in-time artifact. This closes S3-P01; the real A0 adapters follow in S3-P02. Cost (unknown != 0): new_requests 0, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
